description: This recipe is by Nancy Harmon Jenkins and takes 1 hour. Tell us what you think of it at The New York Times - Dining - Food.
title: Rawia Bishara's Vegetarian Musaqa
title_page: Rawia Bishara's Vegetarian Musaqa Recipe - NYT Cooking
text: Use olive oil and vegetable oil instead of all olive oil if you wish. Spice mixture will be more fragrant if you combine whole spices and grind to a powder in a spice grinder or a mortar.
